items.question: Which Parks and Recreaction episodes have extended producers cuts?
items.answer: Rock Show, The Set Up, The Master Plan, Freddy Spaghetti, Harvest Festival, Jerry's Painting, The Fight, Lil' Sebastian, End of the World, The Debate, Bus Tour, Win Lose or Draw, Halloween Surprise, Emergency Response, Second Chance, Flu Season 2, Moving Up, Ron and Jammy, Pie Mary, and One Last Ride.
